window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He's a hockey god...and she's the one who got in his way.</p> <p>I had a foolproof plan.</p> <p>Finish college playing the best sport on earth. Hockey.</p> <p>Get drafted by an NHL team.</p> <p>Make my senator father at least a little proud of me.</p> <p>I was on track to do just that…until Violet Reece and I collided. Literally.</p> <p>Turns out, my plan didn’t account for a night in jail–and the news articles that followed it.</p> <p>Everything fell apart after that.</p> <p>New school, new hockey team. And a resentment like I’ve never felt before directed at the girl who set me off course.</p> <p>Lucky for me, she attends this new school of mine.</p> <p>And there are a thousand ways to ruin her.</p> <p><i>Brutal Obsession</i> is a sizzling, dark college bully romance. Our hero does not grovel under any circumstances.</p> <p>Listener discretion is advised.</p>"; 
